{"sn45.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.22 ","sn45.22:0.2":"3. Micchattavagga ","sn45.22:0.3":"Akusaladhammasutta ","sn45.22:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.22:1.2":"“Akusale ca kho, bhikkhave, dhamme desessami, kusale ca dhamme. ","sn45.22:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn45.22:1.4":"Katame ca, bhikkhave, akusala dhamma? ","sn45.22:1.5":"Seyyathidam—micchaditthi …pe… micchasamadhi. ","sn45.22:1.6":"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, akusala dhamma. ","sn45.22:1.7":"Katame ca, bhikkhave, kusala dhamma? ","sn45.22:1.8":"Seyyathidam—sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.22:1.9":"Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, kusala dhamma”ti. ","sn45.22:1.10":"Dutiyam. "}